        "class": "ital",
        "text": "land ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "is confusing. It was the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "land of the Ciccar, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "just mentioned, which was in flames. As Abraham could see the Ciccar, it must have been at the northern end of the Dead Sea (see Note on ",
