        "text": "Genesis 18:16",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "); and as a violent conflagration was raging throughout it, the site of the cities could not have been submerged (see Note on ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 14:3",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). The violence of the fire is indicated by the last word, which is not the ordinary word for a ",
