        "text": "Exodus 19:18",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", “a furnace,” or “kiln,” for burning lime, or making bricks.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
