        "text": "when God destroyed",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", &c.] This verse contains P’s brief summary of the whole event. This will explain the repetition of the narrative, and the sudden substitution of “God” (",
        "children": []
