        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") for “the Lord” (Jehovah). The expression “God remembered Abraham” would otherwise seem strange after the narrative in 18; but, as a matter of fact, the sentence probably followed after ",
